{"tid":2129354,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新手養貓 有咩要準備？","createTime":"2020-07-28T13:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T06:15:39.000Z","uid":326240,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c2b174e5e40ae5be3db7f257cd6c122eaf27b770","tid":2129354,"uid":326240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T13:55:26.000Z","msg":"見人哋DIY貓窗網，咁我想問點樣開窗？<br />\n有露台嗰啲點算？<br />\n貓糧係咪最好唔好買超市嗰啲，感邊隻牌子好，邊度可以買？"},{"pid":"637342743fb19658ecd57fff96b655fdeea153db","tid":2129354,"uid":272202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:00:22.000Z","msg":"貓糧可以參考呢個post<br />\n<blockquote>貓糧資料庫（8）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1946645\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1946645</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ab7e55c1d728dc29a731a1a5a2b5a094e314a660","tid":2129354,"uid":337986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:01:14.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好買超市貓糧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千祈唔好買超市貓糧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千祈唔好買超市貓糧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推薦：Origen六種魚/紅肉<br />\n罐頭：thrive, ziwi<br />\n一般寵物店都有賣 你可以上網search 完再order<br />\n通常幾百蚊就有得免費送貨"},{"pid":"475cd9122e7af24788fd04bdfa17bdd2d4821ddd","tid":2129354,"uid":103794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c2b174e5e40ae5be3db7f257cd6c122eaf27b770","tid":2129354,"uid":326240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T13:55:26.000Z","msg":"見人哋DIY貓窗網，咁我想問點樣開窗？<br />\n有露台嗰啲點算？<br />\n貓糧係咪最好唔好買超市嗰啲，感邊隻牌子好，邊度可以買？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:02:24.000Z","msg":"窗網 ：<br />\n買12蚊店格仔網裝， 自己綁索帶， 等陣補張相畀你睇<br />\n呢個係最化算嘅方法，仲有其他方法嘅，譬如裝蚊網<br />\n<br />\n如果有露台 我勸你都係唔好養貓喇，好多貓跳樓死， 無日無之 <br />\n實有人話啲窗我唔會開.. 會好小心之類 唉 意外意外 就係意料之外<br />\n<br />\n貓糧：<br />\n超市通常嗰啲都係味精多，成份唔好<br />\n我就通常網上店舖買，滿300免運<br />\n推薦 天下貓貓 （佢地會捐部份收益比義工）<br />\n<br />\n糧食最好： 生肉＞濕糧（主食罐）＞鮮食 加營養粉＞乾糧<br />\n但新手可以濕糧加乾糧餵先，唔係隻隻貓習慣食生肉"},{"pid":"1fde269880a9828fb72df56786cd0db84dc087da","tid":2129354,"uid":337986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:04:02.000Z","msg":"露台都有得裝貓網<br />\n要搵人裝<br />\n貴少少"},{"pid":"054a0b2c18fc3ebb5439365b69803af96c6a83bd","tid":2129354,"uid":326240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"637342743fb19658ecd57fff96b655fdeea153db","tid":2129354,"uid":272202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:00:22.000Z","msg":"貓糧可以參考呢個post<br />\n<blockquote>貓糧資料庫（8）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1946645\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1946645</a></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:04:07.000Z","msg":"唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3190cfe5e062f73e8cc12235632ceb77ccda9a9","tid":2129354,"uid":326240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab7e55c1d728dc29a731a1a5a2b5a094e314a660","tid":2129354,"uid":337986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:01:14.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好買超市貓糧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千祈唔好買超市貓糧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千祈唔好買超市貓糧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推薦：Origen六種魚/紅肉<br />\n罐頭：thrive, ziwi<br />\n一般寵物店都有賣 你可以上網search 完再order<br />\n通常幾百蚊就有得免費送貨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:04:29.000Z","msg":"唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d8ab677c58a2b3c1284c43a3491149bf477feb","tid":2129354,"uid":326240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"475cd9122e7af24788fd04bdfa17bdd2d4821ddd","tid":2129354,"uid":103794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c2b174e5e40ae5be3db7f257cd6c122eaf27b770","tid":2129354,"uid":326240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T13:55:26.000Z","msg":"見人哋DIY貓窗網，咁我想問點樣開窗？<br />\n有露台嗰啲點算？<br />\n貓糧係咪最好唔好買超市嗰啲，感邊隻牌子好，邊度可以買